    div(class="divider")
    div(class="about")
      div(class="aboutTitle") About  
      div(class="aboutDescription") 
        p(class="aboutfntsize") Welcome to the alpha version of Dashboard! Dashboard is a web application that gives users a feed of information in one page so that they never have to get lost again. Know everything within one page. Check your twitter feeds without losing your last read article. Currently still in production and still needs some features implemented! So sit tight and check back later for more cool content.
        p(class="aboutfntsize") Register or Login and explore what we have so far!

    div(class="apiTitle") API's Used 
    div(class="apisblock")
        div(class="apiDescription") New York Times
          img(class="apiPicturenyt" src="./media/newyorktimes.png")
        div(class="apiDescription" id="yahoo" ) Yahoo Stocks Api
          img(class="apiPicturey" src="./media/yahoo.jpg")
        div(class="apiDescription") Twitter Feed Api
          img(class="apiPictureya" src="./media/twitter.png")

    
    div(class="divider")
    div(class="wrapper")
      div(id="main" style="padding:50px 0 0 0;")
      form(id="contact-form" action="/" method="post") 
        h3 Contact Us!
        h4 Fill out the form below, and we'll get back to you as soon as possible.
        div
          label
            span Name:
            input(placeholder="Please enter your name" type="text" tabindex="1" required autofocus)
        div
          label
            span Email:
            input(placeholder="Please enter your email address" type="email" tabindex="2" required)
        div
          label
            span Message:
            textarea(placeholder="Include all the details you can" tabindex="5" required)
        div
          button(name="submit" type="submit" id="contact-submit") Send Email




